.gov.np/image/data/Population/VDC-Municipality%20in%20detail/39%20Syangja_VDCLevelReport.pdf |website=[[Central Bureau of Statistics (Nepal)|Central Bureau of Statistics]] |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141026134818/http://cbs.gov.np/image/data/Population/VDC-Municipality%20in%20detail/39%20Syangja_VDCLevelReport.pdf|archivedate=2014-10-26 }}</ref>\n\n==Education==\nPrimary education is provided by Shree Gandaki Primary School. Secondary education is provided by Rivervalley Mathematics Anon Solution - RMAS{{Citation needed|date=February 2017}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20080226150941/http://www.merosyangja.com/ Mero Syangja]\n*[http://www.chapakotmun.gov.np/en Chapakot Municipality]\n*[http://ddcsyangja.gov.np/en/ District Coordination Committee Office, Syangja, Nepal]\n\n==See also==\n{{Sankhar}}\n\n[[Category:Syangja District]]\n[[Category:Populated places in Syangja District]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox settlement\n<!--See the Table at Infobox settlement for all fields and descriptions of usage-->\n<!-- Basic info  -->\n|name                    = Bhattarai Danda\n|other_name              =\n|native_name             =\n|nickname                =\n|settlement_type         = [[City]]\n|motto                   =\n<!-- images and maps  -->\n|image_map               = {{mapframe|plain=yes|frame=yes|type=point|frame-align=center|zoom=13|marker=marker|marker-color=0050d0}}\n|mapsize                 = \n|map_caption             = \n|pushpin_map             = Nepal Gandaki Pradesh#Nepal\n|pushpin_label_position  = bothumb\n|pushpin_map_caption     = Location of Bhattarai Danda\n|pushpin_mapsize         = 300\n<!-- Location -->\n|subdivision_type        = Country\n|subdivision_name        = {{flag|Nepal}}<!--the name of the country-->\n|subdivision_type1       = [[Nepalese Federal States|Province]]\n|subdivision_name1       = [[Gandaki Pradesh|Gandaki]]\n|subdivision_type2       = [[Dist