b/20150311074048/http://screenproducersaustralia.org.au/news/screen-producers-australia-awards-finalists-announced-2/|archive-date=11 March 2015|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n|Screentime\n|{{Nom}}\n|-\n|[[Australian Screen Sound Guild|ASSG Awards]]\n|Best Sound for a Television Drama Series<ref>{{cite web|url=http://assg.org.au/assg-awards-nominations-2014/|title=ASSG  \u2013  ASSG Awards Nominations 2014|work=ASSG|accessdate=5 May 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150528143656/http://assg.org.au/assg-awards-nominations-2014/|archive-date=28 May 2015|url-status=dead|df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n|''ANZAC Girls''\n|{{Won}}\n|-\n|rowspan=\"8\"| 2015\n|rowspan=\"3\"| [[4th AACTA Awards|AACTA Awards]]\n|Best Cinematography in Television<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.smh.com.au/entertainment/movies/4th-aacta-awards-full-list-of-nominees-20141203-11zde7.html|title=4th AACTA Awards: full list of nominees|work=The Sydney Morning Herald|accessdate=5 May 2015}}</ref>\n|Geoffrey Hall\n|{{Nom}}\n|-\n|Best Sound in Television\n|Tom Heuzenroeder, Des Kenneally, Belinda Trimboli and Pete Best\n|{{Won}}\n|-\n|Best Production Design in Television\n|Scott Bird\n|{{Nom}}\n|-\n|rowspan=\"3\"| [[Logie Awards of 2015|Logie Awards]]<ref>{{cite news|last=Willis|first=Charlotte|url=http://www.news.com.au/entertainment/awards/heres-the-full-list-of-2015-logies-nominations/story-fn8cjmx5-1227273521488|title=Here's the full List of 2015 Logies nominations|publisher=[[news.com.au]]|date=22 March 2015|accessdate=2 April 2015}}</ref>\n|Most Outstanding Mini-Series or Telemovie\n|''ANZAC Girls''\n|{{Nom}}\n|-\n|[[Logie Award for Most Outstanding Newcomer|Most Outstanding Newcomer]]\n|Brandon McClelland\n|{{Nom}}\n|-\n|[[Logie Award for Most Popular New Talent|Most Popular New Talent]]\n|Laura Brent\n|{{Nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[Golden Nymph Award]]s<ref>{{cite web|last=Knox|first=David|url=http://www.tvtonight.com.au/2015/04/aussie-dramas-nominated-at-%E2%80%8Emonte-carlo-tv-festival.html|title=